Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.46,0:22:27.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Yeah upside down, upside down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:31.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}この居場所を終わらせない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:30.86,EDCNchs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}我们如同落叶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:34.66,EDCNchs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}飘零于水面上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:38.16,EDCNchs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}漂泊不知去处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:42.30,EDCNchs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}随波逐流而战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:45.45,EDCNchs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}即便天涯两隔
